00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,880
Where did you learn it, Ms. Zhao?

473
00:32:52,360 --> 00:32:53,120
Guys,

474
00:32:53,520 --> 00:32:54,800
who's the winner

475
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,520
for the water-trace round?

476
00:32:57,360 --> 00:33:00,720
Ms. Zhao, of course.

