00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:10,400
Excellent. Amazing.

482
00:33:13,120 --> 00:33:15,160
The last round is the taste.

483
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:17,080
We may win.

484
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,560
Beiyuan Tea

485
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:22,400
