486
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:24,800
It is the king's tea.

487
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:29,280
A treasure, indeed.

488
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,710
- Bravo.
- Bravo. Bravo.

