00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:43,440
People's spiritual heights are leveled.

506
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,880
So is tea.

507
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:47,920
You don't need the best water and leaf

508
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,400
