00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:25,760
- Bravo.
- Bravo.

536
00:37:27,640 --> 00:37:28,360
We win.

537
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:44,760
Good work.

538
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:47,720
Gentlemen,

539
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,800
in terms of tea ceremony,

